http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/Clean-Kochi-to-spruce-up-city/article14024456.ece

The Corporation of Kochi has launched ‘Clean Kochi 2016’ project beginning with a month-long cleaning drive at Ernakulam market and nearby areas.Mayor Soumini Jain launched the project and Deputy Mayor T.J. Vinod presided over the function held at the market yard.The project will be implemented with the support of residents’ associations, educational institutions, trade and industrial firms and other organisations.Apart from cleaning, all illegally placed advertisements would be removed under the project.Standing committee chairpersons, councillors, Corporation officials, and representatives of Kerala Merchant Chamber and Market Stall Owners Association were present.